text:
Vision: "A caring community that multiplies authentic disciples". This strong communal culture is complemented by Biblical teaching, a balance between traditional and contemporary worship style, and a fervour for the advancement of the Lord's mission in this world.

Morning service at 09:00 at The Cathay (nearest MRT: Dhoby Ghaut).

Afternoon service at 14:30 at Grace S.C.C. Church, 14 Queen St (nearest MRT: Bras Basah).
